{"tid":2230252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教宗方濟各發表新通諭　指無論如何都要拒絕戰爭　疫情證明資本主義失效","createTime":"2020-10-04T22:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T00:29:51.000Z","uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"87431be77e6ef24944ff0ce2cbc96396db3c9e57","tid":2230252,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:35:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%9F%E5%90%84%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E6%96%B0%E9%80%9A%E8%AB%AD-%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E8%AB%96%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%2590%2584%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25AB%25AD-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%2583%25BD%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2588%25AD-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2588%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=eccc26df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%2590%2584%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25AB%25AD-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%2583%25BD%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2588%25AD-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2588%2F&h=ba627498\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%9F%E5%90%84%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E6%96%B0%E9%80%9A%E8%AB%AD-%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E8%AB%96%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88/</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎對全球造成嚴重影響，教宗方濟各在周日發表新通諭，表達了他對後新冠肺炎的預想，他認為，疫情證明資本主義失效，世界需要新型政治，以促進對話及加強團結，而且無論如何都要拒絕戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎對全球造成嚴重影響，教宗方濟各在周日發表新通諭，表達了他對後新冠肺炎的預想，他認為，疫情證明資本主義失效，世界需要新型政治，以促進對話及加強團結，而且無論如何都要拒絕戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n方濟各在題為《眾弟兄》（Brothers All）通諭中表示，無論如何都要拒絕戰爭，這否定了過往天主教以戰爭為合法防御手段的說法，方濟各解釋，今時今日已經難以再用上幾個世紀的標準，去討論正義戰爭（Just War）的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n根據《天主教教理》卷三《在基督內生活》第 2309 條，訂明在五項的嚴格條件，以及道德合法性的嚴格條件的規範下自衞，這些條件包括：侵略者所加予國家或國際社會的傷害應是持續的、嚴重的和確定的；─除訴諸武力以外的其他一切辦法均顯示不切實際或無效；有成功的可靠條件；訴諸武力不會招致比應剷除的惡，有更大的惡及混亂。教理訂明這些是所謂「正義戰爭」的道理中的傳統要素。"},{"pid":"cb3a2ff9929be87538fa6e1787fc61ba990621a2","tid":2230252,"uid":68215,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:37:30.000Z","msg":"諗起有預言話佢係最後一任教宗"},{"pid":"7652a073989f12cd5b999c5217b8f6bcbbd76ffc","tid":2230252,"uid":284432,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:37:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62a690a97adb4faad342aed43e7fc0abfcffb0ec","tid":2230252,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:39:02.000Z","msg":"共產黨"},{"pid":"1e0bfba0aed3143cc3c413678d66622d497a6308","tid":2230252,"uid":71676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:39:29.000Z","msg":"支持無神論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7614785417251ca15c012a50fe0af9548e9831","tid":2230252,"uid":370972,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:40:01.000Z","msg":"資本主義失效???????<br />\n乜嘢結論嚟？"},{"pid":"697e10159e6b92200efa6d3d85b5c1bc70fce302","tid":2230252,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:40:56.000Z","ms